{"tid":2251338,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"DJI Pocket 2 正式發佈","createTime":"2020-10-20T17:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T09:49:16.000Z","uid":24044,"like":2,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5863b2c47290dab1e905eb257fc5debc29105634","tid":2251338,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"連登竟然無人講？<br />\n--------<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/10/20/dji-pocket-2-officially-launched/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F10%2F20%2Fdji-pocket-2-officially-launched%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QUwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=1466588c\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/10/20/dji-pocket-2-officially-launched/</a><br />\n<br />\n潮人新寵物 DJI Pocket 2 終於正式推出，可謂係今個月內繼 iPhone 12 以外另一大受 Gadget 愛好者所追捧的科技產品。上一代 Osmo Pocket 推出時有不少不足之處，如今第二代建立於上一代的成功再將部分不足進行改良，相信必定會更受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dji-pocket-2-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdji-pocket-2-02.jpg&h=1e5a998b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDJI Pocket 2 外觀上與上一代相若，但名字上已經「飛走」了上一代的 Osmo 一詞，變更得為簡單一點。而除了名稱上之外，Pocket 2 硬件功能上已經大大提升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先是鏡頭的像素，上一代只有 1,200 萬像素，而 Pocket 2 已經升級至 6,400 萬像素，CMOS 是 1/1.7 吋 (對比上一代是 1/2.3 吋)。鏡頭角度亦提升至 20 mm 等效焦距 及 f/1.8 光圈鏡頭，比起上一代 26mm 在自拍上更廣闊。而另一樣改善，就是終於支援變焦，有 8 倍變焦能力。<br />\n<br />\n錄影方面，同樣是可拍攝 4K/60fps 影片。並支援 HDR 影片，可提升影片的亮度動態範圍。相比起 Pocket 1，全面升級的混合對焦 2.0 技術讓 DJI Pocket 2 對焦更快及準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDJI Pocket 2 在其他細節方面亦有所提升，像是開機只需 1 秒、關機時預設鏡頭回中、當裝置處於跌落狀態時能迅速感應並及時對雲台進行保護等。另外，拍攝影片過程中可以隨時暫停錄制，為後期製作免去許多剪輯麻煩。此外，裝置及其細小配件均可完整收納至保護殼內，令使用更加簡單方便。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機身雖小巧，但內置功能亦不少，像是支援 Wi-Fi 、藍牙、無線咪高峰接收器、1/4&Prime; 螺紋口、揚聲器及 3.5mm 音訊連接埠集合於一身，支援外接多種配件、支援無線圖傳、支援單機回放影像等功能。此外，DJI Pocket 2 還有增廣鏡、無線咪高峰發射端、防水殼、手機夾、與 Osmo Pocket 通用的加長桿和 ND 濾鏡等配件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dji-pocket-2-03.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdji-pocket-2-03.jpeg&h=082938ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDJI Pocket 2 標準版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dji-pocket-2-04.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdji-pocket-2-04.jpeg&h=6c485503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDJI Pocket 2 套裝版<br />\n售價:<br />\n<br />\nDJI Pocket 2 標準版官方售價 HKD $2,899，包含 DJI Pocket 2、保護殼、迷你搖桿、三腳架轉接元件（1/4&rdquo;），手繩，手機連接頭（Lightning），手機連接頭（USB-C），充電線等。<br />\nDJI Pocket 2 套裝版官方售價 HKD $ 3,999，於標準版基礎上額外附有：微型三腳架、增廣鏡、全能手柄、無線咪高峰防風毛套、無線咪高峰發射端、雙頭充電線等豐富配件。<br />\n發售日期：11月1日，DJI Pocket 2 及套裝版在香港地區正式發售。"},{"pid":"abdb924ab5cef1e6c60daddddc9ca00954a1b4f5","tid":2251338,"uid":24044,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/dji-pocket-2-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2Fdji-pocket-2-01.jpg&h=90d59e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我無第一代，諗住買第2代"},{"pid":"adfb5dbec4997a41cc47b83d90798f97ca0e20d3","tid":2251338,"uid":295230,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"DJI NO"},{"pid":"c0e9567e31fad4a7056f710bceea2a6079150249","tid":2251338,"uid":126329,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"等收腐皮啦你老母"},{"pid":"6b3d37e37a447e95915a084c74b4553bb5edbb1a","tid":2251338,"uid":254371,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13022fae760102c06e597c2e0ad2397281dc52e1","tid":2251338,"uid":123969,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,